Description: egor aids with the process of importing, analysing
    and visualising ego-centric network data. It supports several data formats,
    including the export formats of EgoNet (McCarty 2011), EgoWeb 2.0 (Kennedy 
    et al.) and openeddi (Eddens/ Fagan). egor offers an interactive (shiny) app 
    for the intuitive visulisation of ego-centered  networks. It also includes 
    procedures for creating and visualising Clustered Graphs (Lerner et. al 
    2008).
